Note: This publication has been revised to correct an error in the original version where data from one provider was not included in the national totals for November 2015. The impact on national figures is fairly small. For example 91.3% of patients admitted, transferred or discharged within four hours of arrival in all types of A&E departments in November 2015 was previously reported as 91.4%, and total A&E attendances are now 1,874,234 instead of 1,851,172.
